frameDefinitions: A Killer or Cause causes the death of the Victim.
An Entity changes from a Prior_state to a Post_state in a sequence that follows a pre-defined plan, expectation, or model of change.
An Entity is at a particular stage of its development.
The Creator creates a new entity, the Created_entity, possibly out of Components.
An Developer develops a Product, in some cases for a Company.    '' 'The development of a profitable product will be necessary for the company to stay afloat.
An Agent works on a Project so that it reaches a more advanced and desirable state.
